      "raw_text": "1t is rumored about the court\nhouse today that the grand jury\nand Prosecutor Pugh have sue\nceeded in breaking through the lit\ntie circle of defense that sur\nrounded the facts relating to Judge\nM. J. Gordon's connection with the\nGreat Northern railroad and the\ncourts.\n\n\nThe character of this evidence\nand it's extent cannot be learned.\n\n\nThe rumor is afloat, probably\nstarted by some witness who told\nmore than he wanted to, and then\nadmitted on the outside that the\nJig is up\""
